ould be around 2.5metric\ntonnes, but even larger masses and shorter mission durations can be achieved\nwith some of the more advanced NTP options studied. In all 4 different proposed\nNTP systems and 5 different trajectory scenarios are examined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 16:40:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
