it is improbable\nfor the GCs to reveal tidal features, something that can be tested with future\ndeep observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2020 18:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2020 21:01:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
