originate from them\nin the optimistic cases. In the future, such neutrino counterparts together\nwith gravitational wave observations can be used in a multimessenger approach\nto elucidate in greater detail the evolution and the physical mechanism of SMBH\nmergers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2020 00:12:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 2020 21:23:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-21"}
